Anonymous Code Release for Peer Review

This code is released solely for the purpose of double-blind peer
review of the ICDM 2026 submission "KnowStroke: Bilateral Dual-Channel
Graph Learning with Task-Decoupled Contrastive Supervision for Joint
Post-EVT Risk Prediction".

During the review period, the code may be inspected and run by
reviewers and program committee members. Redistribution, derivative
work, or any use beyond peer review is not granted at this time.

A permissive open-source license will be added in the camera-ready
version of the submission.
